{"tid":605771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"35%市民：林鄭表現冇樣好","createTime":"2018-03-26T03:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T16:47:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"815e567c7dc53a441aa051f2a3eaa5e2e528f71c","tid":605771,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T03:21:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180326/20342968\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180326%2F20342968&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA03Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=8ddb2293\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180326%2F20342968&h=454d30e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180326/20342968</a><br />\n<br />\n35%市民：林鄭表現冇樣好<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】一年前的今日，林鄭月娥以777票當選成為「三低特首」，對手曾俊華選前形容，林鄭是「低民望、低能量、低認受性」，若當選港人未來5年會很難受。一年轉眼過去，泛民、建制派及普羅市民對林鄭又有何評價？身為香港人的你，覺得社會撕裂有修補嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180326/large/a0801a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180326%2Flarge%2Fa0801a.gif&h=1a25056a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180326/large/a0801b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180326%2Flarge%2Fa0801b.gif&h=94aa0289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180326/large/a0801c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180326%2Flarge%2Fa0801c.gif&h=58000217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t未助港人安居　無捍衞法治<br />\n要聞 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t反口拒解決「三座大山」<br />\n要聞 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t避敏感議題惹建制不滿<br />\n要聞 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t梁家傑：靠振英之亂保民望<br />\n要聞 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t商界：社會撕裂氣氛趨緩和<br />\n要聞 3小時前"},{"pid":"bb1ed710c575e848f1f02dfa595bd29c5c25bec5","tid":605771,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T03:35:30.000Z","msg":"佢仲有鄉事既票要找<br />\n<br />\n年頭鄉事團拜已經提林病找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2b5c5c763244f342e0a45262eee8f0c5ac5eab","tid":605771,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"都仲有成班on9港豬覺得佢好"},{"pid":"f097d5223317531e9c865e11b9e70414f159a33d","tid":605771,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T09:25:07.000Z","msg":"毒果民調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae04983edd7dfd249ee1d4245a97c42f84856355","tid":605771,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"呢個垃圾正苦, 識改變<span style=\"color: red;\">企業利得稅成兩級制<br />\n全民就業, 失業率偏低, 係種種有利爭取勞工權益情況下</span><br />\n無趁機會同企業傾勞工條件 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n理財新哲學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">MPF 對沖<br />\n全民退保, 醫保<br />\n勞工假, 銀行假問題<br />\n立法5天工作制<br />\n最高工時<br />\n</span><br />\n有心攪樓市<span style=\"color: red;\">租金管制</span> 唔得咩"}]}